    "text": "JUST ACCEPTED: \"Welfare Costs of Shopping Trips\" has been accepted for publication at The Annals of Regional Science.\n\nThe working paper version is available at https://t.co/sqHqVa8EN7 @SSRN #EconTwitter #shopping",
