    "author_name": "HAKAN YILMAZKUDAY",
    "handle": "yilmazkuday",
    "text": "By using a DSGE model, this paper investigates the effects of international trade costs and alternative inflation targets on the exchange rate determination. https://t.co/zLHcpbaiE8 https://t.co/s5vwsXb041",
