    "author_name": "HAKAN YILMAZKUDAY",
    "handle": "yilmazkuday",
    "text": "This paper investigates the effects of inflation on per capita income growth for 36 developed and developing countries by using structural vector autoregression models that are robust to the consideration of endogeneity by construction. https://t.co/F3u23Ye2U9 \n\nThe results show evidence for heterogeneity of such effects across countries that are shown to be further connected to the strength of their institutions. \n\nWhile the effects of inflation on growth are negative and significant in countries with stronger institutions, they are positive and significant in countries with weaker institutions.",
