    "handle": "yilmazkuday",
    "text": "Introducing and simulating a two-country DSGE model, this paper investigates the role of international trade costs on exchange rate determination under different inflation targets. https://t.co/pchTs2w7Pb https://t.co/kB3ilzqpxy",
